source.title: Atlantis Decoded? Cataclysms, Forbidden History, and Plato‚Äôs Secret Code | Randall Carlson
source.channel: THIRD EYE DROPS with Michael Phillip
source.description:
Atlantis, Plato, sacred geometry, ancient myths, and lost technology and esoteric history.

[ Get your limited edition copy of Giordano Bruno and the Hermetic Tradition Here: https://tinyurl.com/brunoTED ]

Is Atlantis a myth or real history? What does the geological evidence say? What are the hidden layers of wisdom beneath the surface of Plato's text? All of this and much more in this mind meld. 

In this one, @TheRandallCarlson  returns to journey, line by line through one of Plato's Critias to navigate one of history's greatest puzzles: Atlantis. Along the way, we explore the sacred geometry, cosmic cataclysmic cycles, and sacred mysteries encoded in the dialogue. 
More topics:
Why Plato‚Äôs Critias may preserve more than just allegory
The Atlantean blueprint and its connections to sacred geometry
Evidence of lost ancient technology and knowledge systems
How ancient cataclysms and cosmic cycles may explain Atlantis‚Äô fall
What the text reveals about humanity‚Äôs forgotten past and hidden potential
Randall Carlson is a researcher, teacher, and master builder known for his decades of work on catastrophism, sacred geometry, and ancient civilizations. His insights invite us to reimagine not only the origins of Atlantis, but the foundations of human history itself.
